title: Odd Couple
typeOfFood: Ovo, Chinese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. High-end Asian-fusion and Cantonese cuisine restaurant in Saskatoon's Riversdale. Offers a range of traditional as well more modern flavors. Has vegetable-based dishes like the ginger mushrooms, a vegan pho (noodle soup), house-made spring rolls, pad thai with five-spice tofu, tomato curry, Chinese greens wok fry, and a crispy Schechuan tofu with rice.
